<h3>3.4 Software and Hardware Requirements</h3>
<p><strong>Hardware Requirements:</strong>
* Processor: Intel Core i5 or equivalent (Minimum)
* RAM: 8 GB or higher
* Storage: 256 GB SSD
* Internet Connection: Stable connection required for AI API access.</p>
<p><strong>Software Requirements:</strong>
* Operating System: Windows 10/11, macOS, or Linux
* Integrated Development Environment (IDE): VS Code
* Frontend Framework: Node.js, React, Vite
* Backend Framework: Python 3.10+, FastAPI
* Database: MongoDB Atlas (Cloud) or Local MongoDB Compass.</p>
<h3>3.5 Preliminary Product Description</h3>
<p>The Technical Recruiter Platform is a web-based client-server application. It utilizes a React-based Single Page Application (SPA) on the frontend that communicates asynchronously with a FastAPI backend. The application manages user sessions, allowing Candidates to browse jobs and supply resumes which are processed by AI to build an internal profile. HR agents use visually rich dashboards to monitor the influx of candidates and review AI-graded interview reports directly from the system.</p>
<h3>3.6 Conceptual Model</h3>
<p><strong>3.6.a Use Case Diagram</strong></p>
<pre><code>usecaseDiagram
